rComments: Best professor in all my undergrad courses. Absolutely loved his course (it was an elective for me) I highly recommend this guy for his knowledge of global south issues.
Quite enjoyed his class great professor. REally passionate about the economy of latin america I learned a lot from him one of my most favourite classes taken.

He's an excellent professor, but you have to be willing to give the work a lot of thought and to attend all the lectures.  Lectures are packed with information and run in a logical course.  He's exceptionally good at intertwining theory and facts.
Very passionate about Latin American politics and very helpful if you are willing to learn.
